{"tid":2401234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一句說話解釋點解只會有女性主義唔會有男性主義","createTime":"2021-02-09T14:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T15:30:06.000Z","uid":90615,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32f6983c84476e3a70457a2584ff6a175c8ff902","tid":2401234,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"同樣遇上問題<br />\n女人會圍爐怪其他人怪世界逼害佢<br />\n然後逼世界改變就返佢地個套<br />\n男人剩係識硬食 自己去迎合世界"},{"pid":"3014faf9550721664c5c426baa0658aeafbc27b1","tid":2401234,"uid":208323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"因為男權會令人極度憎恨女人<br />\n最後變基佬<br />\n但係變基佬之後發現基佬仲hi過女人<br />\n所以最後會尊重返女人"},{"pid":"52e91d8aab5d461503124b673cd9fd7d44c075a9","tid":2401234,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4c4ee1788a50dd120905eba7f1d191d068a3ba","tid":2401234,"uid":205594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"過多幾十年或者會有。當初女性主義之所以出現，同男人多年嘅壟斷有密切關係。"}]}